<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕節的腳步逐漸逼近，<delay20 />
島上的傢伙們<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />似乎也為了過節而
忙著準備禮物啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay8 />慌慌張張的有夠吵……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay8 />我也沒資格
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說別人就是了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">馬上就是平安夜啦，<delay20 />
你的禮物<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />準備得怎麼樣？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是那個<delay20 />交換禮物用的禮物啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可別忘了包裝咧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那可是要用來交換的，<delay20 />
外表可是很重要的喔，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我問你，<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有看到廣場上的聖誕樹嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那裝飾還真是五彩繽紛啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來有夠華麗的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看到那種東西，<delay20 />就是會讓人
不禁期待起節日啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>